const schemaScripts = ["{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Service\",\"name\":\"Backsplash Installation Sacramento\",\"provider\":{\"@type\":\"LocalBusiness\",\"name\":\"Pro Tiling\",\"telephone\":\"(916) 555-0100\"},\"areaServed\":{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"Sacramento\"},\"description\":\"Kitchen backsplash tile installation in Sacramento including subway tile, mosaic, large-format slab, and custom tile patterns.\",\"serviceType\":\"Backsplash Installation\"}"];
const contentHtml = "<section class=\"page-hero\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"page-hero__content\">\n          <nav class=\"page-hero__breadcrumb\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\">\n            <a href=\"/\">Home</a><span>\u203a</span><span>Backsplash Installation Sacramento</span>\n          </nav>\n          <h1>Kitchen Backsplash Installation in Sacramento, CA</h1>\n          <p>Custom backsplash tile that ties your kitchen together \u2014 installed with precision, clean lines, and zero mess left behind. Serving Sacramento and surrounding communities.</p>\n          <div class=\"page-hero__cta\">\n            <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">Get a Free Estimate</a>\n            <a href=\"tel:9165550100\" class=\"btn btn--outline\">Call (916) 555-0100</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"service-content\">\n          <div class=\"content-body\">\n            <span class=\"section-label\">Kitchen Backsplash Experts</span>\n            <h2>A Backsplash That Actually Makes the Kitchen</h2>\n            <p>The backsplash is one of the most visible surfaces in any kitchen \u2014 and one of the most underinvested. A well-chosen and expertly installed backsplash can tie together countertops, cabinets, and appliances in a way that makes the whole room feel intentional and complete.</p>\n            <p>Pro Tiling has installed kitchen backsplashes throughout Sacramento, Roseville, Elk Grove, and Folsom \u2014 from simple 3-inch subway tile for classic kitchens to full-slab porcelain behind a range for a high-end contemporary look. We bring the same attention to detail to a backsplash job that we do to a full bathroom remodel.</p>\n\n            <img class=\"content-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620626011761-996317702519?w=900&q=80\" alt=\"Custom kitchen backsplash tile installation in Sacramento \u2014 herringbone white tile\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" />\n\n            <h2>Backsplash Styles We Install</h2>\n\n            <h3>Classic Subway Tile Backsplash</h3>\n            <p>Never goes out of style. We install subway tile in all sizes \u2014 3x6, 4x8, 4x12 \u2014 in traditional brick offset, stacked vertical, herringbone, and horizontal stack patterns. The right grout color and joint size changes the whole character of the installation, and we help you dial those choices in during planning.</p>\n\n            <h3>Full-Height Backsplash</h3>\n            <p>Running tile all the way from countertop to upper cabinet \u2014 or all the way to the ceiling \u2014 is a popular upgrade in Sacramento kitchen remodels. It elongates the space, eliminates the painted drywall band, and gives the kitchen a more custom, built-in feel.</p>\n\n            <h3>Large-Format Slab Backsplash</h3>\n            <p>A single-slab or large-tile backsplash with minimal grout lines creates a sleek, modern look that's also easier to keep clean. We install porcelain and natural stone slabs behind ranges and along full runs with precision-cut openings for outlets and switches.</p>\n\n            <h3>Mosaic & Patterned Tile Backsplash</h3>\n            <p>Zellige, encaustic cement tile, glass mosaic, and hand-painted patterned tile all require extra care to install correctly \u2014 especially around the edges and where patterns need to be centered and balanced. This is exactly the type of custom tile work we specialize in.</p>\n\n            <h3>Range Hood Focal Tile</h3>\n            <p>The area directly behind and above a range is the focal point of the kitchen. We design and install feature tile in this zone \u2014 whether that's a dramatic natural stone, a patterned cement tile, or a contrasting material that makes the range hood stand out.</p>\n\n            <h2>What Makes Our Backsplash Installs Different</h2>\n            <p>On a backsplash, details matter more than almost anywhere else \u2014 because you're looking directly at it every day. We take time to:</p>\n            <ul>\n              <li>Center the layout visually, not just mathematically</li>\n              <li>Cut around outlets, switches, and range hoods cleanly</li>\n              <li>Use the correct adhesive for the tile type and substrate</li>\n              <li>Keep grout joints consistent throughout</li>\n              <li>Caulk all inside corners (not grout them) for long-term durability</li>\n              <li>Leave zero adhesive residue on tile faces</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>These are the small things that separate a pro install from an amateur one \u2014 and they're the things Sacramento homeowners notice every single day.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"faq\">\n              <h2 style=\"margin-bottom:8px;\">Backsplash Questions</h2>\n              <div class=\"faq-item\">\n                <button class=\"faq-item__question\">How long does backsplash installation take? <span class=\"faq-item__icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg></span></button>\n                <div class=\"faq-item__answer\"><p>A standard kitchen backsplash is typically a 1\u20132 day job: installation on day 1, grouting and sealing on day 2. More complex projects with mosaic tile, full-height runs, or large slabs may take an additional day. We'll give you a specific timeline based on your kitchen.</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"faq-item\">\n                <button class=\"faq-item__question\">Do you remove existing backsplash tile? <span class=\"faq-item__icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg></span></button>\n                <div class=\"faq-item__answer\"><p>Yes. We handle demo, surface prep (patching, skim coat if needed), and install. We protect your countertops and cabinets during demo and clean up completely at the end of every day.</p></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <aside class=\"service-sidebar\">\n            <div class=\"sidebar-card\">\n              <h3>Get a Free Estimate</h3>\n              <p style=\"font-size:0.875rem;margin-bottom:18px;\">Most backsplash estimates can be done same week. We respond same day.</p>\n              <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn btn--primary\" style=\"width:100%;justify-content:center;\">Request a Quote</a>\n              <a href=\"tel:9165550100\" class=\"btn btn--outline-dark\" style=\"width:100%;justify-content:center;margin-top:10px;\">Call (916) 555-0100</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sidebar-card\">\n              <h3>Backsplash Options</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Subway tile (all sizes)</li>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Large-format slab</li>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Glass & mosaic</li>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Natural stone</li>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Full-height runs</li>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Patterned / cement tile</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sidebar-card\">\n              <h3>Related Services</h3>\n              <div class=\"sidebar-links\">\n                <a href=\"/tile-installation-sacramento\">\u2192 Tile Installation</a>\n                <a href=\"/bathroom-tile-sacramento\">\u2192 Bathroom Tile</a>\n                <a href=\"/shower-tile-installation-sacramento\">\u2192 Shower Tile</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </aside>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta-band\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"cta-band__inner\">\n          <h2>Ready for a kitchen that looks <em>custom-built</em>?</h2>\n          <div class=\"cta-band__actions\">\n            <a href=\"tel:9165550100\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">(916) 555-0100</a>\n            <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn btn--outline\">Free Estimate</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>";
